column4: Alert! My PC suddenly powered off, and now it won't power on again. What happens? May I have lost my files?
Sounds like a hardware problem. Likely your power supply or so
Remember this is only our best guess to the issue. Try with a known good power supply if possible before buying a new one
is ubottu available for others to use
Yes, do:  /msg ubottu Hi                      then you can talk to him. Or visit the tab he's in now
